      <span class="section-label">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:32px;">Commercial Pest Control — FAQs</h2>
      <div style="max-width:800px;">
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Does Wernex provide pest control for restaurants in St. George?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Yes. Wernex provides restaurant-specific pest management programs that meet UDAF and health department requirements. We provide compliance documentation for inspections, offer after-hours service to avoid disrupting operations, and respond same-day for emergencies. Call (435) 673-9503.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">What industries does Wernex serve commercially?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Wernex serves restaurants, hotels, vacation rentals, retail stores, offices, medical facilities, warehouses, food processing plants, storage facilities, and multi-unit residential properties throughout Southern Utah.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Does Wernex provide compliance documentation?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Yes. Wernex provides detailed service reports, pesticide application records, and compliance certificates for health inspections, property management audits, and corporate pest management requirements.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Can Wernex service my business after hours?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Yes. Wernex offers flexible scheduling including early morning, evening, and weekend service appointments to minimize disruption to your business operations.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">How much does commercial pest control cost in Southern Utah?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Commercial pricing depends on facility size, pest pressure, service frequency, and industry requirements. Wernex offers free commercial assessments and competitive pricing. Call (435) 673-9503 for a custom quote.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Explore More</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:24px;">Related Services &amp; Areas</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:16px;max-width:900px;">
        <a href="pest-control-southern-utah.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🌄 Pest Control Across Southern Utah</a>
        <a href="pest-control-vacation-rentals-southern-utah.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🏡 Vacation Rental Pest Control</a>
        <a href="index.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🏠 Wernex Home — St. George Pest Control</a>
        <a href="services.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🛠️ Full Service List</a>
        <a href="pest-control-hurricane-ut.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📍 Pest Control in Hurricane, UT</a>
        <a href="pest-control-washington-ut.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📍 Pest Control in Washington, UT</a>
        <a href="pest-control-near-zion-national-park.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🏞️ Pest Control Near Zion</a>
        <a href="termite-control-st-george.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🪵 Termite Control — St. George</a>
        <a href="contact.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📞 Schedule an Appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section--dark" style="padding:60px 0;text-align:center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color:var(--white);">Protect Your Business — Call Wernex Today</h2>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:16px auto 28px;max-width:55ch;">Free commercial assessments, compliance documentation, and flexible scheduling. Trusted by Southern Utah businesses for over 30 years.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Schedule Free Inspection</a>
        <a href="tel:+14356739503" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg" style="border-color:var(--lime);color:var(--lime);">📞 (435) 673-9503</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FOOTER ═══ -->
</BaseLayout>
